[CovertActionNarrative_FindFaction_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Old Signals"
ActionPreNarrative="Commander, we've been picking up scattered transmissions on an old XCOM frequency. With your permission, I'd like to take a squad and investigate. - CO Bradford"
ActionPostNarrative="Commander, I managed to locate the source of the signals-- a old FOB, manned by an unknown faction. When I introduced myself, they told me that Dr. Hadley, of all people, was waiting to talk. - CO Bradford"

[CovertActionNarrative_RecruitEngineer_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Tech Support"
ActionPreNarrative="We have made contact with resistance sympathizer in one of the megacities. Allowing him to join us would be a security breach, but they're all yours. - Dr. Hadley"
ActionPostNarrative="The sympathizer turned out to be technically-minded, having worked extensively in an ADVENT Mech Bay. They'll be a boon to engineering."

[CovertActionNarrative_RecruitScientist_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Higher Learning"
ActionPreNarrative="Another day, another turncoat. ADVENT is bleeding in the shadows... - Dr. Hadley"
ActionPostNarrative="The sympathizer turned out to be technically-minded, having spearheaded new experimental methodology in an ADVENT Gene Therapy Clinic. They'll be a boon to the labs."

[CovertActionNarrative_GatherSupplies_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Supply Drop"
ActionPreNarrative="One of the teams recently 'liberated' a supply cache but lacked the manpower to retrive it. Send a squad to these coordinates. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="The supply drop was recieved successfully."

[CovertActionNarrative_GatherIntel_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Data Tap"
ActionPreNarrative="The Program has a storied background in communications intelligence. An opportunity has arisen to take advantage of this proficiency."
ActionPostNarrative="The datatap went off without a hitch. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_IncreaseIncome_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Helping Hand"
ActionPreNarrative="Even people in the ADVENT megacities will help. One way, or another. Send a squad to this location and cause a ruckus-- we'll handle the rest. - Dr. Hadley"
ActionPostNarrative="Thanks to your distraction, we secured a number of incursions into enemy dataframes and are prepared to relocate supplies to resistance sites. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_RescueSoldier_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Personnel Extraction"
ActionPreNarrative="We recently got wind of a captured XCOM operative being moved into my zone. I could use a few more boots on the ground to sniff them out. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="Operative located. Transmitting coordinates. - 'Handler 9'"

