[CovertActionNarrative_RemoveDoom_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Sabotage AVATAR Facility"
ActionPreNarrative="Sabotage is one of many specialties. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="All too easy. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_ImproveComInt_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Tactical Education"
ActionPreNarrative="Training is not just about technique, but resources. And the only place in the world with Old-World levels of both is the Program. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="The Resistance will be well-served by these soldiers, Commander. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_ResistanceContact_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Signal Boost"
ActionPreNarrative="We know of several abandoned radio towers in the area. If you can get them running, the resistance might find more support. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="The resistance broadcasts come at all hours of the day in this zone. As they should. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_BreakthroughTech_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Technical Advances"
ActionPreNarrative="I'm surprised you guys don't know about this. If you send me a team, I can organize a raid on the old archives for the reports. - Dr. Hadley"
ActionPostNarrative="Here you are, Commander. Going through those files is a pleasant trip down memory lane. Happy to do it for you. - Dr. Hadley"

[CovertActionNarrative_ResistanceCard_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="New Orders"
ActionPreNarrative="Ultimately, we share the same goal. Let's talk capabilities, and... favors curried. - Dr. Hadley"
ActionPostNarrative="You will find our reach troublingly long-- but for now, it's yours. - Dr. Hadley"

[CovertActionNarrative_AlienLoot_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Scavenge Alien Loot"
ActionPreNarrative="The Program regularly trims the fat off ADVENT patrols for future operations. We ran an op nearby a haven recently; you could send a squad to secure the area and its resources. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="ADVENT tech is rarely useful for us-- hopefully you will find it valuable. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_FacilityLead_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Facility Lead"
ActionPreNarrative="Got a lead on an ADVENT Facility in my local AO, but all of my squads are tied up. Send me some of yours and together we can sniff it out. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="Generally, Hadley prefers we leave the facilities online, but this is your op. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_RevealChosenMovements_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Behind Enemy Lines"
ActionPreNarrative="My operative onboard the Avenger has informed me that the Chosen have been hunting for you in particular, Commander. Troubling, but not unexpected in light of recent events. I have a man with information on <XGParam:StrValue2/!ChosenClass/>'s base of operations, but communications with him are patchy and sporadic. I recommend that you send some soldiers to rendezvous with him and retrieve that intelligence. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="The data indicates <XGParam:StrValue1/!ChosenName/>'s' stronghold is located in <XGParam:StrValue3/!ContinentName/>. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_RevealChosenStrengths_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Find the Stronghold"
ActionPreNarrative="Now that we have the general location, I can bring the full might of the Program against <XGParam:StrValue2/!ChosenClass/>'s stronghold. However, the RECSATs are old and need maintenance. If you can send some men on a raid for parts, we can make this happen. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="We now have satellite confirmation of ADVENT transports entering and leaving a covert base of operations located in <XGParam:StrValue3/!ContinentName/>. We will begin planning for the strike immediately.- 'Handler 9'"

[CovertActionNarrative_RevealChosenStronghold_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Into the Fire"
ActionPreNarrative="In order to enable the strike against the Chosen Stronghold, we'll need to figure out of to breach it. Send some of your men along with my own Operatives to get a feel for the base. - 'Handler 9'"
ActionPostNarrative="We have determined the best plan of entry to <XGParam:StrValue1/!ChosenName/>'s stronghold. Transmitting now. - 'Handler 9'"

[CovertAction_HuntTemplarsP1Template X2CovertActionTemplate]
ActionObjective="Hunt the Templars"

[CovertActionNarrative_HuntTemplarsP1_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Find Them"
ActionPreNarrative="As you might recall, Commander, six days after the Temple Ship crash-landed, I initiated Operation: New World. Unfortunately, there was a lone survivor. Staff Sergeant Lanner was left a mangled wreck, his mind in shambles from my operative's psionic assault, but he managed to limp away during the chaos of the beginning of Operation: Ashes and Temples, Act Three. Only recently have we managed to pinpoint his general location, but we need your manpower to figure out where he's hiding. - Dr. Hadley"
ActionPostNarrative="Excellent. You should be proud of your soldiers, Commander. Keeping up with my operatives is not an easy task. - Dr. Hadley"

[CovertAction_HuntTemplarsP2Template X2CovertActionTemplate]
ActionObjective="Hunt the Templars"

[CovertActionNarrative_HuntTemplarsP2_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Gain Their Trust"
ActionPreNarrative="Mobilizing enough operatives to assault the base head-on and ensure no survivors would take far too long. I have a better idea, and I'll need more of your men to accomplish it. - Dr. Hadley"
ActionPostNarrative="With the help of your soldiers, I have managed to place several operatives as civilians within the Templar compound. One step at a time. - Dr. Hadley"

[CovertAction_HuntTemplarsP3Template X2CovertActionTemplate]
ActionObjective="Hunt the Templars"

[CovertActionNarrative_HuntTemplarsP3_Program X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Lure Them Out"
ActionPreNarrative="Lanner, or Geist, as he is now known, is extremely paranoid, and revealing a vulnerablity remains a challenge. Instead of attacking the compound directly, MILADVISE is giving 98.2 percent odds that leaking the location of the First Contact site will prompt Geist to investigate personally. In order to make it convincing, I'll need some of your soldiers to join mine for one final operation. - Dr. Hadley"
ActionPostNarrative="The trap is primed. The bait is set. All that remains is spring it. I will send my best, and if you do the same, victory is assured. - Dr. Hadley"
